 "obj_dw_fcastle_cafe_slash_Other_11_gml_285_0": "* (He makes a small and knowing smile^1. You feel your cup trembling...)\\S0/%",
 "obj_dw_fcastle_cafe_slash_Other_11_gml_314_0": "* Boss. Thanks you^1, I was able to relocate here./",
 "obj_dw_fcastle_cafe_slash_Other_11_gml_315_0": "* Now I can do big uppercuts at the dinner table all day long./%",
 "obj_dw_fcastle_cafe_slash_Other_11_gml_320_0": "* HYAAAAAAAAAHHHH!!^1! But quietly to not bother the other customers./%",
 "obj_dw_fcastle_cafe_slash_Other_11_gml_328_0": "* Boss!^1? I'm trapped at a table with this crembulous dog!?/",
 "obj_dw_fcastle_cafe_slash_Other_11_gml_329_0": "* Fine..^1. I guess I'll use my special attack^1, \"falling in love.\"/%",
 "obj_dw_fcastle_cafe_slash_Other_11_gml_334_0": "* Who's a cute little guy!^1? Who's a special little guy!?/",
 "obj_dw_fcastle_cafe_slash_Other_11_gml_335_0": "* ..^1. that's my problem with this blumbo^1, he never tells me the answer.../%",
 "obj_dw_fcastle_cafe_slash_Other_11_gml_364_0": "* FRAIND..^1. MADE BLOOM^1. NOW I PROTECT FRAIND./%",
